short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Opens a new Google meet in a new tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Make sure to pin the icon after installation.

Upon clicking on the icon, it will simply create a new google meet in a new tab.

Streamline your virtual meetings with our Chrome extension, 'Meet & Greet'! With just a single click on the extension icon, open a new Google Meet in a new tab instantly. Save precious time by bypassing the hassle of manually creating meetings, and dive straight into productive discussions with ease.
